name: Shanghai Silk Halter Dress
description: In crimson or black stretch silk with exquisite lotus hand applique detail at the neckline. Truly a stunning evening dress for your special occasion. In supple & soft satin silk.

name: London, 1967 Dress
description:
This form fitting long sleeve mini dress features eyelet fabric that seductively reveals what's underneath.  Can be worn on its own or layered over another top or mini-dress. High neck and slight bell sleeves convey elegance and class. Retro styling.

100% Cotton.

name: Totem Halter Dress
description:
The sleek Totem dress exudes luxury in animal print stretch velvet, with striking hand applique of fossil-shell, macrame and black pebble beads. In tiger stripe (velvet), python (cotton lycra), and peacock (stretch silk, hand-printed). 

Collar ornaments of Indian Ocean fossil shells or hand-carved totems from Papau New Guinea make this a unique and stunning art dress.

Pair with Arabesque sandals in silver leather $145.

name: Aztec Dress
description: The Aztec dress is stunning with ruffled neck and chest, bead and macrame applique, and a cloud motif on handpinted batik. This is an art dress sure to impress at your next special outing.

name: Galaxy Dress
description: The Galaxy is the ultimate bad girl's dress.  100% leather with brass grommet details, it fits like a glove and wears like serious trouble.

name: Erin Blouse
description: The Erin tunic exudes drama with oversized brass grommets and lacing on the front.  In stretch black satin and stretch tiger velvet, with ornate Celtic cross contrast embroidery on the back.  Also in grey stretch denim, with leather cross detail on back.

name: Star Dress
description: The Star dress is wearable treasure.  Blending silky microfiber lycra with leather details and an unforgettable mesh star motif, it is a revealing, sophisticated dress with transformative power.

name: Silk Flower Dress
description: Luxurious stretch black silk with contrast white silk flowers at neckline and hem creates a sweet, sexy dress for a freespirited evening.

name: Baroque Flower Dress
description: The Baroque is an exquisite art dress with many subtle details.  Boning inside keeps its shape and stays in place.

name: Mermaid Two Piece Dress
description: The Mermaid is a gorgeous silk chiffon outfit.  Ruching on the hips and waist allow it to hug your curves perfectly.  With hand stitched details and abalone shell buttons.

name: Cinch Dress - Elemental Print
description: Embody the elements in these colorful dresses-- fire, earth, ocean, and cloud.  Comfortable double layer mesh with ruching on the sides and carefree bell sleeves.

options.name: blue ocean with sleeves (single layer) large

name: Crown Jewels Dress
description: Stretch silk body-hugging dress with ruching at chest and arms.  Intriguing crystal jewel applique.

name: Ingenue Two Piece Dress
description: The Ingenue is made in a selection of airy batik fabrics.  Hip-hugging ruched skirt accentuates your figure while the soft cotton is comfortable on your skin.

black with white polka dots medium
black with white polka dots large

name: Paris Silk Dress
description: The Paris is a sleek stretch silk dress with a plunging V back accentuated by contrast color edges and piping.  Elegant and surprising, you're sure to be a hit at the next party.

name: Bustier Dress
description:
The Bustier dress is your perfect little black dress for every occasion.
Slinky black micro poly fabric slips comfortably against the skin, and white contrast stitching highlights the bust and seamlines.  Stretches to hug your curves. Sexy and lightweight for travel!

name: Grand Prix Leather Halter
description: Leather halter top with crossover motorcycle style front zipper and spaghetti straps.  Corset lacing in back adjusts to fit your shape perfectly.

name: Survival Dress
description: You will survive.  Make sure everyone knows it with the deviously seductive Survival dress in black stretch silk.  Rhinestone applique.  The plunging back and spaghetti straps make this dress slinky and sexy as it gets.

name: Custom Lotus Print Dress
description: Traditional Balinese designs are screenprinted in limited batches for this gorgeous dress.  Cotton/lycra blend stretches to fit your shape.  3/4 length sleeves and calf length hem.

name: Bolero Shirt
description:
An elegant dress shirt with understated flair.  Dashing.  Custom stitched embroidery detailing.

100% cotton

name: Bagatelle Dress
description: Great stretch silk evening dress with elegant draped chiffon on the sides.

name: Dragon Rider Leather Utility Belt
description: Intricate leather details make this leather holster belt one of a kind.  Durable and badass, hold all your small belongings in one place.

name: French Country Dress
description: Smooth and sexy stretch microfiber with contrast stitching and fine  French lace insets in white or black.

name: Indian Ocean Halter
description: Cotton halter top with high neckline. Snaps at neck.  Oversize brass grommets on back for a corseted effect. Available in black eyelet or handprinted Javanese batik.

name: Indian Ocean Blouse
description: Oversize grommets accentuate the front of the Indian Ocean Blouse, adjust as desired. Available in white eyelet, black eyelet, and handprinted sarong fabrics.

name: Indian Ocean Skirt
description:
Flirty chiffon ruffles adorn the hem of this summer dress.  Matches the Indian Ocean halter and blouse.

Cotton.

black eyelet with red lining large

name: Retro Halter Dress
description: These simple cotton halter dresses evoke 1950's charm.  Choose from a myriad of colors and patterns, go out and have fun!

name: Ruched Leggings
description:
Sexy and comfortable, these leggings are perfect paired with a long tunic or dress.  Ruching detail adds intrigue.

Made of slinky black lycra.

name: Jungle Shirt
description: Mens' shirt for dress or casual wear features unusual cut out designs with rough edges inspired by jungle life. Cotton and linen.

name: Sea of Japan Dress
description: The Sea of Japan dress epitomizes elegance with stretch silk and use of the traditional Indonesian handmade lace technique, krawang.  All lace details are painstakingly sewn and cut out by hand.  In this dress you embody refined and understated sensuality.

name: Bonita Dress
description: The Bonita is artistically designed with a plunging square neckline in body-hugging stretch silk.  Brass studs at waist give a belted effect and add a touch of glamour.

name: Jungle Fever Dress
description: The unusual one-armed design of the Jungle Fever dress is daring, fun, snd sexy!  Ruching up the arm and sides of the dress give it extra body.  Made of super comfortable lycra to fit a variety of sizes easily.

name: Mod Leather Mini Skirt
description:
Sexy little leather mini skirt.  

Note: Sizes for this skirt run small.  Order one size larger than you usually would.

name: Marrakesh Dress
description: The custom fabric handprinted in North African interlace and grommet details give this dress impact.

name: Ring Dress
description: Unique dress design with circle cut outs at waistline that feature large rings that suggest an architectural flair.

name: Maghrib Skirt
description: The Maghrib is a flirty skirt with a row of ruffles at the hem and custom Arabesque embroidey. Flamenco look. Lined.

name: White Leopard Logo Crop Shirt
description: Comfortable, versatile foundation piece for yoga and everyday.  Also great as a layering piece that shows off your waistline.

name: Carib Pants
description: Easy, breezy white mens' pants. For your next adventure near warm seas.

name: Jungle Pants
description: Casual and adventurous mens' pants with cut out designs finished with rough edges.

name: Lotus tank
description:
Simple tank top with our custom print designs.  Pair with the Lotus Pants for an elegant look.

Cotton lycra.

name: Lotus Pants
description:
Stretch yoga-style pants with custom print.  V-waistband gives a very flattering fit.  Snug through knee with boot cut hem. Pairs well with the Lotus Tank Top.

Cotton lycra.

name: Prada Skirt
description: The body of the Prada skirt is a cotton eyelet fabric with small holes that allow the hand-printed gold and black lining to peek through.

name: Applique Pants
description: Bell cut pants with sparkle lace applique around side slit.  Dazzling.

name: Bustier Top
description: The Bustier top is a sexy piece for everyday wear.  Pair with jeans or a skirt, can be dressed up or down.  Stretch denim gives support and flexibility.

name: White Leopard Logo Dress
